 (1,0) – (4,0);
 (-4,0) circle (3pt);
 (-1,0) circle (3pt);
 (1,0) circle (3pt);
 (4,0) circle (3pt);
tikzpicture
center

*Interpretation:* All numbers more than 1 unit from 0 but less 
than 4 units from 0—the "ring" between distance 1 and distance 4.
